info.author: T Blackstone
classifiers: Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules
info.name: inspyre-toolbox
requires_dist: python3-xlib<0.16,>=0.15; sys_platform == "linux" or sys_platform == "linux2" or sys_platform == "darwin"
info.summary: Inspyre Toolbox is a collection of tools designed to simplify programming tasks, reducing repetitive code. Initially for internal use at Inspyre Softworks, it benefits other developers too with features like a live timer, humanize class for numerical operations, extended argparse, process management, and miscellaneous Python helpers.
